        </table>
      </div>

      <h2>The Conversion Infrastructure Gap</h2>
      <p>Here's the single biggest finding from our analysis of home-service ad accounts: <strong>80% of businesses running active Facebook ads have no automated follow-up system.</strong></p>
      <p>They spend $500–$3,000/month on ads, capture a lead form or phone call, and then... nothing. No email sequence, no SMS reminder, no nurture campaign. The lead either books on the first call or disappears forever.</p>
      <p>Home-service businesses that add a simple 3-touch email/SMS follow-up sequence after the initial contact see a <strong>40–60% increase in booked appointments</strong> — without spending a single extra dollar on ads.</p>

