      <h2>3-Step Follow-Up System Every Trade Business Needs</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Touch 1 (Same Day):</strong> Phone call + SMS confirmation within 2 hours of lead submission</li>
        <li><strong>Touch 2 (Next Day):</strong> Personalized email with service overview, pricing range, and a photo of similar work</li>
        <li><strong>Touch 3 (Day 3):</strong> SMS reminder + offer of a free estimate or inspection</li>
      </ol>
      <p>This isn't complicated. But almost no one does it — which is exactly why it works.</p>
